name: Confidentiality of computer software and database structures Bank Information; Protocol, Quality Control or Methodology; Sample Sharing; Local DNA Laboratories; Disposal
text: [§844D-85]  Confidentiality of computer software and database structures.  To maintain the computer system security of the state DNA database and data bank identification program, the computer software and database structures used by the DNA laboratory of the department to implement this chapter are confidential. [L 2005, c 112, pt of §1]
